23 WHEREAS, Roger Colbert, formerly of Paragould, Arkansas, passed away on
24 February 4, 2025, at the age of sixty-seven (67); and
25
26 WHEREAS, Roger Colbert was born on January 28, 1958, in Poplar Bluff,
27 Missouri; and
28
29 WHEREAS, Roger Colbert earned a degree in political science from
30 Arkansas State University and was a brother in Pi Kappa Alpha, and afterward
31 earned his Juris Doctorate from the University of Arkansas at Little Rock's
32 William H. Bowen School of Law; and
33
34 WHEREAS, Roger Colbert made Paragould his home and used his formidable
35 grasp of the law to practice in areas including real estate, corporations,
36 financial institutions, and estates; and
